## Current Objective
Migrate all API and Function invocations within `src/*` away from `httpsCallable` or [fetch](file:///Users/cristiankalexai/Progetti/standlo.com/src/components/layout/canvas/CanvasCatalogSidebar.tsx#38-161) towards the centralized API client [src/lib/api.ts](file:///Users/cristiankalexai/Progetti/standlo.com/src/lib/api.ts) (using `callGateway`), resolving `401` errors and `cloud:validate` failures.

